{
  "name": "srs-writer-plugin",
  "displayName": "SRS Writer",
  "description": "AI-powered Software Requirements Specification writer for VSCode.",
  "version": "0.5.7",
  "publisher": "Testany",
  "repository": {
    "type": "git",
    "url": "https://github.com/Testany-io/srs-writer-plugin.git"
  },
  "bugs": {
    "url": "https://github.com/Testany-io/srs-writer-plugin/issues"
  },
  "homepage": "https://github.com/Testany-io/srs-writer-plugin#readme",
  "engines": {
    "vscode": "^1.102.0"
  },
  "categories": [
    "AI",
    "Chat"
  ],
  "activationEvents": [
    "onStartupFinished"
  ],
  "main": "./dist/extension.js",
  "icon": "media/logo.png",
  "files": [
    "dist",
    "rules",
    "media",
    ".templates",
    "LICENSE",
    "README.md",
    "CHANGELOG.md"
  ],
  "contributes": {
    "chatParticipants": [
      {
        "id": "srs-writer",
        "name": "srs-writer",
        "description": "Intelligent SRS document generator with natural language understanding",
        "isSticky": true,
        "commands": [
          {
            "name": "create",
            "description": "Create a new SRS document"
          },
          {
            "name": "edit",
            "description": "Edit existing SRS document"
          },
          {
            "name": "lint",
            "description": "Check document quality"
          },
          {
            "name": "help",
            "description": "Show help information"
          },
          {
            "name": "new",
            "description": "Start a fresh conversation session"
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "commands": [
      {
        "command": "srs-writer.help",
        "title": "SRS Writer: Help"
      },
      {
        "command": "srs-writer.status",
        "title": "SRS Writer: Show Status"
      },
      {
        "command": "srs-writer.startNewProject",
        "title": "SRS Writer: Start New Project"
      },
      {
        "command": "srs-writer.toggleAIMode",
        "title": "SRS Writer: Toggle AI/Fallback Mode"
      },
      {
        "command": "srs-writer.forceSyncContext",
        "title": "SRS Writer: Force Sync Context"
      },
      {
        "command": "srs-writer.selectBranchForFolders",
        "title": "Select Git Branch for Folders View",
        "icon": "$(git-branch)"
      }
    ],
    "_menus_note": "🚀 分支切换按钮功能已暂时隐藏 - 详细信息见下方注释块",
    "_branch_switcher_feature": {
      "_status": "TEMPORARILY_HIDDEN",
      "_reason": "功能完整但暂时不发布到发布版本",
      "_hidden_date": "2024-01-XX",
      "_original_config": {
        "view/title": [
          {
            "command": "srs-writer.selectBranchForFolders",
            "when": "view == workbench.explorer.fileView && srs-writer:foldersViewEnhanced",
            "group": "navigation"
          }
        ]
      },
      "_implementation_files": [
        "src/core/FoldersViewEnhancer.ts - 主要实现类",
        "src/extension.ts:177 - 命令注册",
        "package.json:205-208 - 命令定义（仍保留）"
      ],
      "_restore_instructions": "要重新启用此功能，请将 _original_config 中的内容复制到 menus 对象中",
      "_notes": [
        "所有相关代码都完整保留，只是移除了UI入口",
        "命令 srs-writer.selectBranchForFolders 仍可通过命令面板调用",
        "功能包括：Git分支选择、智能切换、项目会话同步等"
      ]
    },
    "menus": {},
    "configuration": {
      "type": "object",
      "title": "SRS Writer",
      "properties": {
        "srs-writer.useAIOrchestrator": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "default": true,
          "description": "启用AI智能工具代理（新架构）"
        },
        "srs-writer.internetSearch.tavilyApiKey": {
          "type": "string",
          "default": "",
          "description": "Tavily Search API密钥",
          "markdownDescription": "Tavily AI Search API密钥（推荐国际用户使用）。\n\n**获取方式**：\n1. 访问 https://tavily.com\n2. 注册账号并获取免费API密钥\n3. 将密钥填写到此处\n\n**注意**: 配置后立即生效，无需重启。"
        },
        "srs-writer.internetSearch.bingApiKey": {
          "type": "string",
          "default": "",
          "description": "Bing Search API密钥（需要Azure账号）",
          "markdownDescription": "Microsoft Bing Search API密钥（Azure Cognitive Services）。\n\n**获取方式**：\n1. 访问 https://azure.microsoft.com/services/cognitive-services/bing-web-search-api/\n2. 创建Azure账号并订阅Bing Search API\n3. 获取订阅密钥（Subscription Key）\n4. 将密钥填写到此处\n\n**注意**: 需要有效的Azure订阅。"
        },
        "srs-writer.internetSearch.baiduApiKey": {
          "type": "string",
          "default": "",
          "description": "百度搜索API密钥（API Key）",
          "markdownDescription": "百度AI搜索服务API密钥（推荐中国大陆用户使用）。\n\n**获取方式**：\n1. 访问 https://ai.baidu.com/ai-doc/SEARCH/\n2. 注册百度账号并创建应用\n3. 获取API Key和Secret Key\n4. 将API Key填写到此处，Secret Key填写到下方配置项\n\n**注意**: 需要同时配置API Key和Secret Key才能使用。"
        },
        "srs-writer.internetSearch.baiduSecretKey": {
          "type": "string",
          "default": "",
          "description": "百度搜索API密钥（Secret Key）",
          "markdownDescription": "百度AI搜索服务Secret Key。\n\n**安全提示**：\n- 此为敏感信息，请妥善保管\n- 不要在公开场所分享此密钥\n- 需要与API Key配合使用"
        },
        "srs-writer.knowledge.localPaths": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "default": [],
          "description": "本地知识库路径列表"
        },
        "srs-writer.requirementScaffold.schemaPath": {
          "type": "object",
          "default": {
            "SCHEMA_PATH": "config/schemas/requirement-entity-schemas.yaml"
          },
          "description": "需求实体Schema文件路径配置",
          "properties": {
            "SCHEMA_PATH": {
              "type": "string",
              "description": "需求实体Schema文件路径"
            }
          }
        },
        "srs-writer.projectSwitching.excludeDirectories": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "default": [
            "templates",
            "knowledge",
            "node_modules",
            ".git",
            ".vscode",
            "coverage",
            "dist",
            "build"
          ],
          "description": "切换项目时要排除的目录列表",
          "markdownDescription": "在切换项目功能中要排除的目录名称列表。这些目录不会出现在项目选择列表中。\n\n**默认排除**：\n- `templates` - 用户模板目录\n- `knowledge` - 知识库目录\n- `node_modules` - Node.js依赖\n- `.git` - Git仓库\n- `.vscode` - VSCode配置\n- `coverage` - 测试覆盖率报告\n- `dist` - 构建产物\n- `build` - 构建产物"
        },
        "srs-writer.rag.enterprise.enabled": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "default": false,
          "description": "启用企业RAG知识库检索功能",
          "markdownDescription": "启用企业RAG知识库检索功能。\n\n启用后，AI可以通过 `customRAGRetrieval` 工具访问您的企业知识库。\n\n**注意**：需要同时配置服务器地址和认证信息。"
        },
        "srs-writer.rag.enterprise.baseUrl": {
          "type": "string",
          "description": "企业RAG服务器基础URL",
          "markdownDescription": "企业RAG服务器的基础URL地址。\n\n**示例**：\n- `http://192.168.1.100:8080`\n- `https://rag.company.com`\n\n**注意**：请确保URL可以从VS Code所在网络环境访问。"
        },
        "srs-writer.rag.enterprise.appKey": {
          "type": "string",
          "description": "企业RAG应用密钥（App Key）",
          "markdownDescription": "企业RAG系统的应用密钥。\n\n**安全提示**：\n- 请确保密钥的安全性\n- 不要在公开场所分享此密钥\n- 建议定期更换密钥"
        },
        "srs-writer.rag.enterprise.appSecret": {
          "type": "string",
          "description": "企业RAG应用秘钥（App Secret）",
          "markdownDescription": "企业RAG系统的应用秘钥。\n\n**安全提示**：\n- 此为敏感信息，请妥善保管\n- 不要在版本控制中提交此配置\n- 建议定期更换秘钥"
        },
        "srs-writer.rag.enterprise.defaultDatasetId": {
          "type": "string",
          "description": "默认数据集ID",
          "markdownDescription": "企业RAG系统的默认数据集ID。\n\n**说明**：\n- 当AI调用RAG检索时，如果未指定数据集ID，将使用此默认值\n- 可以在具体调用时通过参数覆盖此设置\n- 请确保此数据集ID在您的RAG系统中存在"
        },
        "srs-writer.syntaxChecker.enabled": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "default": true,
          "description": "启用语法检查工具",
          "markdownDescription": "启用 syntax-checker 工具对 Markdown 和 YAML 文件进行语法检查。"
        },
        "srs-writer.syntaxChecker.markdown.aEnabled": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "default": true,
          "description": "启用 Markdown 语法检查"
        },
        "srs-writer.syntaxChecker.markdown.bMode": {
          "type": "string",
          "enum": [
            "all",
            "standard",
            "no",
            "custom"
          ],
          "default": "standard",
          "description": "Markdown 检查模式",
          "markdownDescription": "选择 Markdown 检查模式：\n\n- **all**: 执行所有 markdownlint 检查项\n- **standard**: 执行必要的检查项（推荐）\n- **no**: 关闭所有 markdownlint 检查\n- **custom**: 自定义模式，使用下方的自定义规则配置"
        },
        "srs-writer.syntaxChecker.markdown.zCustomRules": {
          "type": "object",
          "default": {},
          "description": "自定义规则配置（仅在 Custom 模式下使用）",
          "markdownDescription": "当选择 Custom 模式时，可以配置具体的 markdownlint 规则。\n\n**使用方法**：\n1. 将上方 Mode 设置为 'custom'\n2. 在此处配置具体规则\n\n**示例配置**：\n```json\n{\n  \"MD001\": true,\n  \"MD007\": { \"indent\": 4 },\n  \"MD033\": { \"allowed_elements\": [\"br\", \"details\", \"summary\"] },\n  \n**规则编号及释义**：\n[查看完整的 markdownlint 规则文档](https://github.com/DavidAnson/markdownlint/blob/main/doc/Rules.md) "
        },
        "srs-writer.syntaxChecker.yaml.enabled": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "default": true,
          "description": "启用 YAML 语法检查"
        },
        "srs-writer.syntaxChecker.yaml.level": {
          "type": "string",
          "enum": [
            "basic",
            "standard",
            "strict"
          ],
          "default": "standard",
          "description": "YAML 检查级别",
          "markdownDescription": "选择 YAML 检查级别：\n\n- **basic**: 只检查基础语法错误\n- **standard**: 检查语法 + 基本结构问题（推荐）\n- **strict**: 检查语法 + 结构 + requirements.yaml 特定规则"
        },
